Trade Marketing Chief - CIKARANG - PT AJE Indonesia
Trade Marketing Chief - CIKARANG  -
Trade Marketing Chief - CIKARANG
Responsibilities
TRADE MARKETING CHIEF will coordinating and executing the distribution, price, and promotion activities that are appropriate to the geographical area, channels and sales points, in order to align with the company’s profitability objectives and generating purchase habits of the company’s brands in the final consumer according to positioning guidelines. Making contacts that are external to the company allowing for the development of brands within his work area.Coordinating and supervising appropriate task execution of the staff under his/her responsibility.Keeping the work team fully and adequately trained, in coordination with the Human Resources area.Control of material and/or promotions.Developing the marketing plan and budget for the areas under his/her responsibility.Executing and following the established Marketing Plan.Contacting advertising agencies, promotions, mass media, and Public Relations according to established needs and/or instructions of his/her immediate supervisor.Coordination and organization of events and public relations related to the brand in the areas under his/her responsibility.Developing printed and design advertising elements that link directly with business and marketing and the marketing processes that must be implemented in the company (advertising, corporate identity, marketing, marketing management). According to the resources allocated for the plan.Coordination of marketing activities focused on brand development at sales point (follow-up, analysis, evaluation, and budgeting). Requirements Candidate must possess at least a Bachelor's Degree, Master's Degree / Post Graduate Degree in Economics, Business Studies/Administration/Management, Marketing, Commerce or equivalent.Required skill(s): resources management, plans & budgets, advertising & events, Marketing & product strategies, business strategies, market strategies.At least 3 year(s) of working experience in the related field is required for this position, preferably from consumer or food companies.Applicants must be willing to work in Lippo Cikarang.Preferably Manager / Assistant Managers specializing in Marketing/Business Development or equivalent.Required language(s): Bahasa Indonesia and English, understand Spanish would be an advantage
Requirements
